data.description: This Gorgeous 4 bedroom home is conveniently located with easy access to I-35 and only 20 minutes from downtown OKC, this move in ready home in Edmond offers a fantastic opportunity to be in the charming subdivision of Faircloud Hills where this thriving community is active with walkers and bicycle riders. This lovely home includes 3.5 baths along with an office/flex room. It features modern comforts and tasteful design, situated in East Edmond and known for its close proximity to shopping, dining and entertainment options and quick access to I-35.  The main level welcomes you with a grand entrance, crown molding, wood floors, double sided fireplace, and stylish shutters.  The kitchen features granite countertops and stainless appliances.  The primary suite includes double sinks, soaking tub, walk-in shower and French doors leading to the back patio.  Upstairs there are three bedrooms with two full bathrooms and a bonus room that can serve as a playroom or study. The 4th bedroom upstairs could be a bonus room and has its own full bathroom and walk-in closet.  Included is a storage building in the backyard.  Faircloud  will have you enjoying any of the neighborhood amenities such as the greenbelts, ponds, playgrounds, basketball court and picturesque walking trails!
